<p rend="chapter">Ganthārambhakathā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="1"><hi rend="paranum">1</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Sammā <pb ed="M" n="0.0001" /><pb ed="V" n="0.0001" /> sammābhisambuddhaṃ, dhammaṃ dhammappakāsanaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Saṃghaṃ saṃghuttamaṃ loke, vanditvā vandanārahaṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="2"><hi rend="paranum">2</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"><hi rend="bold">Nāmarūpaparicchedaṃ,</hi> pavakkhāmi samāsato;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Mahāvihāravāsīnaṃ, vaṇṇanānayanissitaṃ.</p>
